name: Effishient
description:
Catch as many fish in a limited time. 

Known issue: The game sometimes runs out of memory and crashes when played in browser. You can download a standalone build! (Windows Only)

Submission for Mini Jam 91: UFO

Game by Villfuk02, sounds and music by Gornemant.

Try to beat my highscore of 3065.

Arrow keys or WASD to move, Space to reverse beam, R to upgrade/restart.
